{{TennisEventInfo|1997|Qatar Open| | date=December 30, 1996 &ndash; January 6 | edition=5th | champs={{flagicon|USA}} [[Jim Courier]] | champd={{flagicon|NED}} [[Jacco Eltingh]] / {{flagicon|NED}} [[Paul Haarhuis]] }}
The '''1997 Qatar Open''', known as the '''1997 Qatar [[Mobil]] Open''' for sponsorship reasons, was a [[tennis]] tournament played on [[Hardcourt|outdoor hard courts]] at the [[Khalifa International Tennis Complex]] in [[Doha]] in [[Qatar]] and was part of the [[ATP International Series|World Series]] of the [[1997 ATP Tour]]. The tournament ran from December 30, 1996, through January 6, 1997.
==Winners==
===Men's Singles=== {{main|1997 Qatar Open &ndash; Singles}} {{flagicon|USA}} '''[[Jim Courier]]''' defeated {{flagicon|GBR}} [[Tim Henman]] 7&ndash;5, 6&ndash;7<sup>(5&ndash;7)</sup>, 6&ndash;2 * It was Courier's 1st title of the year and the 25th of his career.
===Men's Doubles=== {{main|1997 Qatar Open &ndash; Doubles}} {{flagicon|NED}} '''[[Jacco Eltingh]]''' / {{flagicon|NED}} '''[[Paul Haarhuis]]''' defeated {{flagicon|SWE}} [[Patrik Fredriksson]] / {{flagicon|SWE}} [[Magnus Norman]] 6&ndash;3, 6&ndash;2 * It was Eltingh's 1st title of the year and the 33rd of his career. It was Haarhuis's 1st title of the year and the 32nd of his career.
==External links== * [http://www.qatartennis.org/ Official Website] * [http://www.atpworldtour.com/Tennis/Tournaments/Doha.aspx ATP Tournament Profile]
