The '''2019 [[Canoe Slalom World Cup]]''' will be a series of five races in several canoeing and kayaking categories organized by the [[International Canoe Federation]] (ICF). It will be the 32nd edition.
== Calendar ==
The series will open with World Cup Race 1 in [[Lee Valley White Water Centre|Lee Valley]], [[England]] (14–16 June) and it will end with the World Cup Final in [[Prague-Troja Canoeing Centre|Prague]], [[Czech Republic]] (6–8 September).<ref>{{cite web|title=ICF Events Calendar|url=https://www.canoeicf.com/event-calendar|website=CanoeICF.com|accessdate=23 February 2018}}</ref>
