The '''Brazilian Tennis Confederation''' ({{lang-pt|Confederação Brasileira de Tênis}} or CBT) is the governing body of tennis in [[Brazil]]. CBT is responsible for the organization of events such as the [[Brasil Open]] and for representing tennis players in Brazil.
