[[File:Garm-stadium.jpg|thumb|right]]'''Gharm Stadium''' is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[Gharm]], [[Tajikistan]].  It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and was renovated after the [[Tajik Civil War]].  The stadium has a capacity of approximately 3,000 people.

